@startuml
' Issue #22
' Related ADRs: ADR-0011, ADR-0012
' Guardrail: planned sequence; messages are not API contracts.

title Intake até DocumentEnvelope - planejado

actor "Usuário / canal" as Source
participant "Inbox / Intake" as Intake
participant "Documents" as Documents
participant "Files" as Files
database "Metadados" as DB
collections "Object storage" as Objects
participant "Processing" as Processing
participant "Audit" as Audit

Source -> Intake : entrega arquivo + contexto
Intake -> Intake : validar limites e calcular SHA-256
Intake -> Files : registrar original
Files -> Objects : armazenar objeto imutável
Objects --> Files : object reference + integrity
Files --> Intake : FileObject
Intake -> Documents : materializar documento
Documents -> DB : Envelope + versão + referência
DB --> Documents : IDs/version
Documents -> Audit : DocumentMaterialized
Documents -> Processing : solicitar processamento
Processing --> Documents : job reference
Documents --> Intake : envelope + estado
Intake --> Source : recebimento confirmado

note over Intake, Documents
  Materialização documental ocorre aqui.
  Nenhuma interpretação ou operação financeira é aceita neste ponto.
end note

@enduml

